Description:
WOW! THIS ONE YOU MUST CHECK OUT
"Undoubtably one of the best buys in Officer."
Located only minutes from Cardinia train station, shopping centre and some of the finest schools in the area, there is no arguing the location is as good as it gets. On top of this, 21 Hampshire Street is a well-proportioned 3-bedroom home with plenty of room in the backyard.
Featuring:
- 3 good-sized bedrooms, master with en-suite;
- Open plan living/dining room at the rear of the house;
- Study at the front of the house;
- Well appointed modern kitchen with a earthy, natural feel;
- Ducted heating and split system cooling;
- Double car garage with remote control access and internal door to the inside of the home;
- Alfresco, garden shed and still enough room to play in the backyard.
Ready to be sold.
Ray White prides itself on being as accurate as possible however anyone considering purchasing the property should undertake their own due diligence to confirm the above.

PEACE AND TRANQUILITY IN HARMONY
Opposite quiet parkland and positioned in front of native trees and open space is a house that is close to everything. Walking distance to Bridgewood Primary School, Officer Secondary School and close to Cardinia Train Station plus the future retail hub of the Officer postcode.
It's incredible property features:
- 4 large bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Theatre room;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Modern kitchen with waterfall stone bench tops and walk-in pantry;
- Genuine hardwood flooring;
- Heating and cooling;
- Alfresco with decked panels and built-in bbq;
- Good-sized block.
