CLEAN AND COSY IN CRANBROOK
"With little competition among buyers - get in and snap yourself a great purchase before the market bounces back."
Ray White is currently taking private inspections through one of Officer's more appealing properties. Located in the Arcadia Estate, the four-bedroom home is walking distance from Cardinia Train Station, shopping centre and both primary and secondary schools.
Backing on to a peaceful waterway and adjacent to the tranquil lake, the property at 4 Cranbrook is well-positioned.
With new carpets recently installed, landscaped yards and a good coat of paint layered throughout, you won't have to lift a finger before moving in.
Featuring:
- 4 bedrooms; master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Modern kitchen;
- Heating and cooling;
- Alfresco overlooking backyard and creek;
- Double car garage with remote access;
- Landscaped yards.
